<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Sat, 11 Apr 2026 14:03:23 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title>胡佛水坝近景</title><link>https://some.pics/69da54a80ba65</link><description>&lt;p&gt;胡佛水坝，在前往拉斯维加斯的途中可见。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Aerial view of a dam system in a mountainous canyon with a large concrete arch dam holding back blue water, surrounded by rocky terrain and a highway bridge crossing the canyon above." height="2920" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/mihobu/69da54a80ba65.jpg" width="2920"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://mihobu.some.pics"&gt;@mihobu&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 Apr 2026 14:03:23 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>归途中的737-MAX8</title><link>https://some.pics/69da47fd4addf</link><description>&lt;p&gt;在结束了图森市的九周行程后，我正乘坐一架机龄五年的737-MAX8型客机，经拉斯维加斯转机返回哥伦布市的家中。这张照片拍摄于起飞后不久。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A Southwest Airlines aircraft wing and engine are visible in the foreground, photographed from a passenger window during flight above a thick layer of white clouds under a blue sky." height="4284" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/mihobu/69da47fd4addf.jpg" width="4284"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://mihobu.some.pics"&gt;@mihobu&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 Apr 2026 13:09:20 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>蓝岭山脉日出</title><link>https://some.pics/69da3358e3b57</link><description>&lt;p&gt;蓝岭山脉上的日出。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A serene landscape of rolling hills at sunset, layers of mist soften the scene. The sky transitions from pale orange to pink, creating a tranquil atmosphere." height="3710" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/dhester/69da3358e3b57.jpg" width="5920"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://dhester.some.pics"&gt;@dhester&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 Apr 2026 11:41:15 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>塔科阿河火车风光</title><link>https://some.pics/69da1e328fd6c</link><description>&lt;p&gt;从火车上看到的塔科阿河景色。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A serene riverside scene with clear water reflecting a bright blue sky and lush green trees lining the banks, creating a peaceful, natural setting." height="2893" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/dhester/69da1e328fd6c.jpg" width="3857"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://dhester.some.pics"&gt;@dhester&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 Apr 2026 10:11:01 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>麦凯斯维尔甜点店</title><link>https://some.pics/69da1e0431042</link><description>&lt;p&gt;甜美的艾玛琳芝士蛋糕店，是我们在乔治亚州麦凯斯维尔这座古雅小镇探访的特色店铺之一。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Cozy cheesecake shop with wood decor; three customers, one at a fridge, two seated. Counter with menu displays in the background. Warm and inviting atmosphere." height="2810" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/dhester/69da1e0431042.jpg" width="3747"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://dhester.some.pics"&gt;@dhester&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 Apr 2026 10:10:17 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>